data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This stunning residence features 4 spacious bedrooms, 3 modern bathrooms, and a half bath, all spread across 2378 sqft of living space on a 0.24-acre lot. With plenty of room for families and guests, this home includes convenient amenities like a sprinkler system, porcelain floors, and quartz countertops, adding a touch of luxury to your everyday living. The high ceilings and extended covered patio create the perfect setting for relaxation and entertainment. Nestled in a peaceful cul-de-sac, this private sanctuary is also conveniently situated near scenic trails, parks, shopping, and more. Plus, with foam insulation on both the attic and all exterior walls, this energy-efficient home stays cool in the summer and warm in the winter. Move in with absolute peace of mind, as this home comes fully equipped with all appliances, including a refrigerator, cook top/convection oven, dishwasher, washer, and dryer. Enjoy your new home with ease and comfort!
